				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227428" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1546269230 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">31 Dec 2018 15:13</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4104311">
									

<p>Howdy.</p>
<p>Now that the dust has settled on the gift exchange a little, I thought it was a good time to post. This tale was written by the request of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dentixvoxel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721769); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4721769&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="dentixvoxel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4721769)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dentixvoxel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721769); return false;">dentixvoxel</a></span>, who provided the following prompt:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Anything with 2726-A or 049. Or maybe something bird related! Any Bird SCPs? I'm down with 'em! like SCP-3466! Format doesn't matter!</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I'm not too familiar with SCP-2726, and I feel like SCP-049 has been written many, many times before by much more skilled hands than I. However, SCP-3466, and bird SCPs gave me an idea.</p>
<p>Featured here are not one, not two, but three bird skips:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1505">SCP-1505</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-2106">SCP-2106</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3466">SCP-3466</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Additionally, the tale features <a href="/wilson-s-wildlife-solutions-hub">WWS</a>, and is part of the <a href="/those-twisted-pines-hub">Those Twisted Pines Canon</a>.</p>
<p>Special Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;">DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tawny0" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2244665); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2244665&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="tawny0" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2244665)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tawny0" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2244665); return false;">tawny0</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1349098); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1349098&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="Jekeled" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1349098)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1349098); return false;">Jekeled</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546269230" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span> for assistance during the drafting phase.</p>
<p>Thank you for the prompt, dentix. Have a happy new year, my dude.</p>
<p><em>JC</em></p>

