														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4105022">
									

<p>Second Wilson's Wildlife Solutions / Twisted Pines article, and both came out of the art exchange! Woot!</p>
<p>I really like this, and I guess this counts as Wilson's interacting with the Serpent's Hand as well, which means we can mark <em>that</em> GoI interaction down (there's an ongoing plan to have WWS interact with all GoIs). Outside of my own agenda though, this is just straight up good. I had the pleasure of critiquing it, and it's a nice, neat little story about the Hand bribing a Wilson's member to release an SCP from Site-64. It's cool, and has a good number of birds in it, so yay for that!</p>
<p>Birb love +1</p>

